StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETDEGREE
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETDEGREE(cDegree OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cDegree FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT Degree_table.idDegree, Degree_table.degreeName, Degree_table.length,&lt;br/&gt; Degree_table.degreePrerequisites, Degree_table.idFaculty&lt;br/&gt; FROM Degree_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getDegree;
